# JSON Parser

Parses a JSON expression.

# Examples

"processors" : {
	"myjson" : {
		"type" : "json",
		"config" : {
			"output" : "jsondata",
			"input" : "${jsonline}"
		}
	}
}

# Configuration parameters

  • input : Expression to be parsed
  • output : Output field to store the JSON object
